 (in years) between successive occurrences of earthquakes in a certain region
 follow a geometric distribution
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p\left(x|\theta\right)=\left(1-\theta\right)^{x}\theta,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,x=0,1,2,3,\ldots,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,0<\theta<1,
\]

